{"tid":934920,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"好心約人交收就唔好放飛機/ 遲到啦","createTime":"2018-12-09T15:39:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-09T16:56:53.000Z","uid":129145,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"aa145765db81405f9a5e45a53469a26b510d7e07","tid":934920,"uid":129145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T15:39:05.000Z","msg":"借人AC<br />\n係DC Fever約左個人交收PS4 (約埋右), 去到今日再confirm果陣, 又話自己返左大陸要遲D, 都心諗係咪玩野架啦。點知冇啦啦又搬個阿婆出黎可以幫手係佢樓下交收又盛, 好啦當敬老, 點知條仆街未夠鐘已經係度催, 攪到我身水身汗跑上條斜路, 去到佢屋苑又要人下一分鐘出現係佢屋企樓下, 點知最後又係放飛機玩野既仆街, 仲比佢block 埋 <br />\n<br />\n搵搵下發現佢已經唔係第一次放人飛機, Wechat仲係D美容雞icon <br />\n<br />\n我都知自己衰ON9 架啦, <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但唔該約左人交收真係唔好放飛機同要準時, 比少少責任感啦。</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NOtrD1x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNOtrD1x.jpg&h=15cdfae0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rrX0Jtd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrrX0Jtd.jpg&h=e67cc6e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/12/09/233544_c5e0cc55dc1c25ee94986e2676af6424.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F12%2F09%2F233544_c5e0cc55dc1c25ee94986e2676af6424.jpg&h=9f330b4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nWzyi1z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnWzyi1z.jpg&h=043b2cc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/39a2cmz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F39a2cmz.jpg&h=6b78b412&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5Gv9BOf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5Gv9BOf.jpg&h=af85ea08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gguVxmA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F